title: OCVarsity updates from tonight's football games
text:
OCVarsity updates from tonight's football games October 02, 2015 6:48 PM | Print Story | E-Mail Story OCVARSITY.COM OCVarsity makes it easy for you to get updates from our reporters from all of tonight's Orange County high school football games. 
Fans can keep track of the games by: 
1.) follow us on Twitter (@OCVarsity) and look for the hash tag #ocv updates. 
2.) go to the OCVarsity homepage and follow the score updates as they appear in our Twitter feed. 
If you're at a game tonight, send us a tweet about the game that includes #ocvupdates and it might end up being included in our retweets. 
Once the games end, make sure you visit OCVarsity.com to check out all of our game stories, photos, scores and video.
